This room doesn't require any previous rooms or modules to be completed and is intended to be an entry point in learning about AI. However, knowledge of cyber security basics, such as common attacks, threat modeling, and defensive strategies will enhance your understanding. Familiarity with basic programming concepts and statistical thinking can also be beneficial.

